" variable name refactoring for local and global scopes
" move te cursor to a variable name and pres gr o gR to apply the refactoring
nnoremap gr gd[{V%:s/<C-R>///gc<left><left><left>
nnoremap gR gD[{V%:s/<C-R>///gc<left><left><left>


